{
  "stem": "21812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was-- as I said, there was constant turmoil and demonstrations and counter-demonstrations, and then Hitler marched in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what it was like was that the first memory I have is of the-- the bombers coming in, flying in formation over-- over Vienna, and flying low.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In those days, they flew low anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the squadrons coming in, because the airport with just [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] again, 15 or 20 minutes away, by-- at the most, by car.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we heard the-- the tanks and the troops.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We could hear that all day and all night, or maybe longer than that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a-- there was a presence of fear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fear actually settled in at that, when I think back, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- I mean, we started to be afraid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when before, we really hadn't been.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were anxious, but we were not afraid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that point, you became afraid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he came in a few days later and made that speech at the Heldenplatz, the Hero's Place, and-- which is near the-- the inner castle, the-- the castle in-- in the inner city.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't know, maybe 200,000 people gathered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was about 15 minutes walking distance from where I lived, and you could hear the 'Heil Hitler' very clearly, that distance, welcoming him to-- into Vienna.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it-- it was discussed and it was discussed of-- of beginning to talk about leaving the country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you see, my father wanted to leave even in '36, or '35 or '36, because of the economic situation, which just before, an earlier problem, after he lost his job.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And his brothers were here in the United States.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
